61
00:04:29,073 --> 00:04:32,009
但在没弄清楚前 我们不能冒生命危险
but until we know why,we're putting our lives at risk.

62
00:04:32,010 --> 00:04:33,022
我不会留下他不管的 Sayid
I'm not leaving him, Sayid.

63
00:04:33,023 --> 00:04:36,014
-我们还有选择  -这就是Jack
-We may not have a choice.  -It's Jack.

64
00:04:37,068 --> 00:04:40,042
第一次见到他时 他冒着生命危险
The first time I saw him,he was risking his life

65
