Alex 求你了
Alex, please.

153
00:11:59,014 --> 00:12:01,025
Ben 你醒了吗?
Ben, you awake?

154
00:12:07,076 --> 00:12:09,076
我要进来了
I'm coming in.

155
00:12:11,042 --> 00:12:12,079
什么事?
What is it?

156
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,076
是Austen和Jarrah
It's Austen and Jarrah.

157
00:12:14,077 --> 00:12:17,094
他们在这里他们找到我们了
They're here. Somehow they found us.

158
00:12:18,012 --> 00:12:19,026
他们现在在哪里?
Where are they now?

159
00:12:19,027 --> 00:12:21,081
我们把他们关押在我的地方
We captured them.We're holding 'em over at my place.

160
00:12:21,082 --> 00:12:23,005
要我帮你...
Want me to help you get out...

161
00:12:23,006 --> 00:12:25,053
不 把他们分开 我要知道他们是怎么找到我们的
Separate them.I want to know how they found us.

162
00:12:25,054 --> 00:12:27,035
那Juliet和Shepard呢?
What about Juliet and Shepard?

163
00:12:27,036 --> 00:12:29,042
-明天...  -你别操心了 走吧
-Tomorrow...  -Let me worry about that. Just go.

164
00:12:29,043 --> 00:12:31,017
好吧
Got it.

165
00:12:31,018 --> 00:12:32,047
Richard 等一下
Richard, wait a minute.

166
00:12:32,048 --> 00:12:34,048
我在外面等你
I'll wait outside.

167
00:12:39,089 --> 00:12:43,056
我要你把从Tallahassee来的人带来
I want you to bring me the man from Tallahassee.

168
00:12:44,005 --> 00:12:47,035
-你要他做什么?  -照做就是了
-What do you need him for?  -Just do it. Now.

169
00:12:47,036 --> 00:12:49,036
好吧
All right.

170
00:12:57,053 --> 00:13:00,012
"从tallahassee来的人"? 这是什么
"The man from Tallahassee"? What is that

