不 John 我们没有
No,John,unfortunately,we don't have a code

173
00:13:03,053 --> 00:13:06,088
"有个男人在衣橱里用枪指着我女儿"这种暗号
for"there's a man in my closet with a gun to my daughter's head,"

174
00:13:06,089 --> 00:13:09,056
很明显 我们应该有的
although we obviously should.

175
00:13:09,059 --> 00:13:13,024
Sayid身上有个背包
He had a pack with him.

176
00:13:14,035 --> 00:13:16,079
我要她帮我拿来
I want her to retrieve it.

177
00:13:17,070 --> 00:13:19,029
好的
Okay.

178
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,095
但你应该知道John 我女儿最近很恨我
But you should know,John,my daughter currently hates me,

179
00:13:21,096 --> 00:13:24,035
