so I'm not sure holding me hostage is your best option...

180
00:13:24,036 --> 00:13:26,036
爸爸!
Dad!

181
00:13:27,012 --> 00:13:29,012
我会帮你去拿的
I'll get your bag.

182
00:13:40,018 --> 00:13:42,053
我在找那种惊艳的
I'm looking for something really stunning,

183
00:13:42,054 --> 00:13:45,058
能吸引所有人眼球的那种
something that would grab everyone's attention on the table.

