Well, I guess this is it.

431
00:33:16,049 --> 00:33:21,030
谢谢你遵守你的诺言 Ben
Thank you, Ben,for keeping your promise.

432
00:33:58,014 --> 00:33:59,083
站在那里别动!
Hold it right there!

433
