把手举起来!
Get your hands up!

434
00:34:01,019 --> 00:34:04,041
趴下!我说趴下!
Get down! I said get down!

435
00:34:15,007 --> 00:34:17,056
你在这里干什么 John?
What are you doing here, John?

436
00:34:17,057 --> 00:34:19,057
