What did you do?

439
00:34:53,033 --> 00:34:55,093
告诉我不是你干的
Tell me you didn't do it.

440
00:34:55,094 --> 00:34:57,002
你在说什么?
What are you talking about?

441
00:34:57,003 --> 00:34:59,048
告诉我你没有杀那个孩子
Tell me that you didn't kill that kid!

442
00:34:59,049 --> 00:35:00,048
什么?
What?

443
00:35:00,049 --> 00:35:02,095
你认为我和Peter的死有关吗?
You think I had something to do with Peter's death?

444
00:35:02,096 --> 00:35:04,066
我告诉你结束这一切
I tell you to end things with his mother,

445
00:35:04,067 --> 00:35:06,023
接下来 他就死了!
and the next thing you know, he's dead!

446
00:35:06,024 --> 00:35:07,081
John请你冷静一点
John, now calm down, please.

447
00:35:07,082 --> 00:35:10,020
想想你自己说的 我为什么要杀Peter呢?
Think about what you're saying.Why would I kill Peter?

448
00:35:10,021 --> 00:35:11,026
他盯上你了!
He was on to you!

449
00:35:11,027 --> 00:35:15,005
我干这行很久了 我不会害怕一个毛头小子的
I've been doing this for a long time.I'm not sweating some rich kid.

450
00:35:15,006 --> 00:35:16,026
那为什么你还在这里?
Then why are you still here?

451
00:35:16,027 --> 00:35:18,003
-你的意思是?  -我让你离开这里
-What do you mean?  -I tell you to leave.

452
00:35:18,004 --> 00:35:19,073
你告诉我你会离开的
You tell me you're gonna leave town.

453
00:35:19,074 --> 00:35:22,002
为什么你还在这里?!
Why are you still here?

454
00:35:22,018 --> 00:35:25,064
听着John 老实对你说
Now listen, John,I'll be honest with you.

455
00:35:26,004 --> 00:35:27,053
我没有兑现诺言
I didn't end it.

456
00:35:27,054 --> 00:35:29,028
我想干下去
I was looking for an angle.

457
00:35:29,029 --> 00:35:32,039
我想在我退休前捞一笔
I wanted to make some money before I skipped out.

458
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:34,059
但后来发生了这事
But then all this happened.

459
00:35:34,060 --> 00:35:38,053
Peter死了 一切都落空了
Peter died, and everything just went straight into the tank.

460
00:35:39,042 --> 00:35:41,052
她受到很大的打击
She's devastated.

461
00:35:41,097 --> 00:35:44,011
她取消了婚礼
She's called off the wedding.

462
00:35:44,012 --> 00:35:46,065
已经无利可图了 John
There's no profit in it, John.

463
00:35:46,066 --> 00:35:49,066
我是一个骗子 但不是杀人犯
I'm a con man, not a murder.

464
00:35:51,072 --> 00:35:54,022
她取消了婚礼?
She called off the wedding?

465
00:35:54,088 --> 00:35:57,057
她说她做不到
She said she couldn't deal with it.

466
00:35:57,058 --> 00:35:58,097
她需要独自面对
She needs to be alone.

467
00:35:58,098 --> 00:36:01,065
如果我现在打电话给她
So if I were to call her right now,

468
00:36:01,066 --> 00:36:04,022
这就是她要告诉我的?
that's what she would tell me?

469
00:36:06,006 --> 00:36:08,079
电话就在那边 John
Phone's right over there, John.

470
00:36:14,044 --> 00:36:16,068
她的号码是...
What's her numb...

471
00:36:24,077 --> 00:36:28,056
Locke我们知道你不想听到这个消息 但是...
Mr. Locke, we know this isn't what you want to hear, but...

472
00:36:28,057 --> 00:36:30,062
你父亲逃走了
Your father's gone.

473
00:36:30,088 --> 00:36:33,054
他去了墨西哥 在你们那次相遇后...
We know he fled to Mexico shortly after your...

474
00:36:33,055 --> 00:36:36,098
然后就消失了
encounter, then he disappeared.

475
00:36:36,099 --> 00:36:41,013
我很抱歉 他也许在这个世界的任何地方
I'm sorry, but he could be anywhere in the world right now.

476
00:36:42,059 --> 00:36:44,059
好了 探长们 今天就到此为止
All right, detectives,that's enough.

477
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:47,032
Locke先生 今天有活干了
Mr. Locke has work to do today.

478
00:36:48,071 --> 00:36:51,093
如果有什么消息我们会通知你的
We'll let you know if anything develops.

479
00:36:53,071 --> 00:36:57,070
今天我们有好多事要做
We have got ourselves quite a day ahead of us, my friend.

480
00:36:57,071 --> 00:37:00,016
你终于可以起床了
It's finally time to get you up out of that bed.

481
00:37:00,017 --> 00:37:01,081
不 我不想
No. I don't want to.

482
00:37:01,082 --> 00:37:04,016
这可没有选择
I don't remember asking.

483
00:37:08,098 --> 00:37:10,063
现在
Now...

484
00:37:10,064 --> 00:37:12,082
大多数人一开始都不想坐这玩意儿
Most people struggle with this at first,

485
00:37:12,083 --> 00:37:14,083
但别担心
but don't worry.

486
00:37:14,084 --> 00:37:17,006
你会习惯的
You'll get used to it.

487
00:37:17,081 --> 00:37:20,079
不 求你了 我做不到
No, please. I can't do this.

488
00:37:20,091 --> 00:37:24,004
你从八楼摔下来 并幸存了下来
You fell eight stories and survived.

489
00:37:24,005 --> 00:37:26,011
我不想听到 有什么你做不到的
I don't want to hear about what you can't do.

490
00:37:26,012 --> 00:37:27,025
好了
Now let's go.

491
00:37:27,026 --> 00:37:28,065
会没事的
It's gonna be all right.

492
00:37:28,066 --> 00:37:29,075
一切都会好的 John
It's gonna be fine, John.

493
00:37:29,076 --> 00:37:32,032
-来吧  -不 我不能...
