494
00:37:37,065 --> 00:37:39,088
很好
You're fine...

495
00:37:41,028 --> 00:37:43,008
行了
There we go.

496
00:37:43,009 --> 00:37:45,034
行了 伙计
There you go, buddy.

497
00:37:46,009 --> 00:37:48,016
看见了?
See?

498
00:37:48,029 --> 00:37:50,060
也没那么糟 不是吗?
Wasn't that bad, was it?

499
00:37:50,061 --> 00:37:52,086
我一会儿就回来 伙计
Be right back, buddy.

500
00:38:30,055 --> 00:38:34,017
John你真的说到做到了
Well, John,you've really gone and done it now.

