不 先生
No, sir.

508
00:39:05,042 --> 00:39:09,024
你还记得吗?John 当你叫我骗子的时候...
Do you remember earlier, John,when you called me a cheater...

509
00:39:09,087 --> 00:39:13,007
当你说我不配待在这岛上的时候...
When you said I didn't deserve to live on this island? Well, get this--

510
00:39:13,008 --> 00:39:16,000
当我和Jack握手的时候
There I was, shaking hands with Jack

511
00:39:16,001 --> 00:39:18,054
我想方设法不让他离开这座岛
and thinking I'd give almost anything to come up with a way to stop him from leaving,

512
00:39:18,055 --> 00:39:21,073
因为如果他离开的话
because to let him go

513
00:39:21,074 --> 00:39:24,081
那会是一个软弱的信号 一个失败的信号
would be a sign a weakness,of failure, of defeat.

514
00:39:24,082 --> 00:39:25,097
我的人都看在眼里
My people would see that.

515
00:39:25,098 --> 00:39:27,091
他们会知道的
They would know it,

516
00:39:27,092 --> 00:39:30,012
