and that, John, would be the end of me.

517
00:39:30,013 --> 00:39:32,013
但如果我杀了他...
But to kill him...

518
00:39:33,054 --> 00:39:35,054
那才是欺骗
That would be cheating,

519
00:39:35,055 --> 00:39:37,061
因为我的人知道 我许下诺言
because my people also heard me make a promise,

520
00:39:37,062 --> 00:39:40,001
如果我打破诺言...
and to break my word...

521
00:39:40,060 --> 00:39:43,043
他们还是会归咎于我的
that would be the end of me, too.

522
00:39:46,022 --> 00:39:50,076
而这时你出现了 John...
And then you came striding out of the jungle, John...

523
00:39:52,017 --> 00:39:55,055
并实现了我的梦想
to you make my dream come true.

524
00:39:57,048 --> 00:40:02,004
你不是又想和我说那个神奇的盒子了吧?
You're not gonna start talking about the magic box again, are you?

525
00:40:03,014 --> 00:40:07,091
不John 我要带你去看那里面到底有什么
I'm gonna show you what came out of it.

526
00:40:19,091 --> 00:40:21,075
当我那时问你 你是否很痛苦
When I asked you earlier if it hurt

527
