他就是你要炸毁潜艇的原因 是吗?
He's the reason you destroyed the submarine, isn't he?

536
00:40:51,037 --> 00:40:53,021
你害怕了
You're afraid.

537
00:40:53,022 --> 00:40:56,052
你怕他了 而这是唯一一个他找不到你的地方
You're afraid of him, and this is the one place he can never find you.

538
00:40:56,053 --> 00:40:58,062
这是唯一他来不了的地方
This is the one place he can never get to.

539
00:40:58,063 --> 00:41:01,002
你想要我做什么?
What do you want from me?

540
00:41:03,054 --> 00:41:06,026
我不知道这是怎么发生的...
I don't know how it happened...

541
00:41:07,024 --> 00:41:11,041
但你能和这座岛交流 John
But you seem to have some communion with this island, John,

542
00:41:11,042 --> 00:41:14,054
而这让你变的特别重要
and that makes you very, very important.

543
00:41:15,001 --> 00:41:17,023
你不知道自己在说什么
You have no idea what you're talking about, of course,

544
00:41:17,024 --> 00:41:21,028
但经过一段时间你会更好的去理解事物的
but in time you'll have a better understanding of things.

545
00:41:22,026 --> 00:41:24,026
那么我想要什么呢?
So what do I want?

546
00:41:25,002 --> 00:41:27,041
我想帮助你 John
I want to help you, John.

547
00:41:29,002 --> 00:41:31,004
为什么?
Why?

548
00:41:31,053 --> 00:41:34,097
因为我在轮椅上 而你不是
Because I'm in a wheelchair,and you're not.

549
00:41:40,069 --> 00:41:42,086
